inputs.ffmpeg_command: ffmpeg -i {input1} -filter_complex "[0:v]trim=start=0.5:end=4.5,setpts=PTS-STARTPTS, scale=1080:1080 [v0]; [1:v]trim=start=0.5:end=4.5,setpts=PTS-STARTPTS, scale=1080:1080 [v1]; [v0] [v1] concat=n=2:v=1:a=0[outv]" -map "[outv]" -an -c:v libx264 -crf 18 -preset veryfast {output}

nodes.title: FFmpeg Command Runner
widgets_values: ffmpeg -i {input1} -filter_complex "[0:v]trim=start=0.5:end=4.5,setpts=PTS-STARTPTS, scale=1080:1080 [v0]; [1:v]trim=start=0.5:end=4.5,setpts=PTS-STARTPTS, scale=1080:1080 [v1]; [v0] [v1] concat=n=2:v=1:a=0[outv]" -map "[outv]" -an -c:v libx264 -crf 18 -preset veryfast {output}
